{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"case","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","role":"symbol","externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeVertical","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Enumeration Case"},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":[" If a text's language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out vertically."]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"abstract":[{"text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingMode","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeVertical":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"}}}